    {
      "id": "46405152_68861947",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/strimzi/templates/metrics-configmap.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 8,
      "line": 17,
      "message": "You could rename the file to just configmap.yaml and use the following.\n\n{{- if .Values.metrics.enabled }}\napiVersion: v1\nkind: ConfigMap\nmetadata:  {{- include \"common.resourceMetadata\" . | nindent 2 }}\ndata: {{ tpl (.Files.Glob \"resources/metrics/*\").AsConfig . | nindent 2 }}\n{{ end }}\n\nAnd then in the kafka.yaml ref the cm using:\n\n      valueFrom:\n        configMapKeyRef:\n          name: {{ include \"common.fullname\" . }}\n          key: kafka-metrics-config.yml",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 4405,
        "name": "Fiachra Corcoran",
        "display_name": "Fiachra Corcoran (EST)",
        "email": "fiachra.corcoran@est.tech",
        "username": "efiacor"
      },
      "updated": "2023-03-24 11:53:52.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
